collection.name: Apostles: Genesis
collection.description:
The genesis Apostle collection by BYOPills. Apostles are 3D, game-ready avatars ready to take on the Metaverse. Apostles are required to enter the BYOVERSE, our future metaverse, and will be able to generate $TRYP, the utility token that powers the BYOPills ecosystem. Link to BYOLand: [BYOLand](https://opensea.io/collection/byoland)
Link to BYOKEY: [BYOKey](https://opensea.io/collection/byokey)
Link to BYOPills, our original collection: [BYOPills](https://opensea.io/collection/byopills)
